text: Henrique Johann (born 11 October 1956) is a Brazilian rower. He competed in the men's coxed four event at the 1980 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1956 births Category:Living people Category:Brazilian male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Brazil Category:Rowers at the 1980 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
